    "class": "name"
   },
   "html": "\n[ くらはし・そうぞう ]"
  },
  {
   "type": "raw",
   "tag": "div",
   "attrs": {
    "class": "prof"
   },
   "html": "\n幼児教育指導者、東京女子師範学校教授、日本保育学会会長、教育刷新委員会委員"
  },
  {
   "type": "raw",
   "tag": "table",
   "attrs": {
    "class": "lt"
   },
   "html": "<tbody><tr><td class=\"lt\"><a href=\"02k.html\">一覧　（カ）</a></td><td class=\"lt\"><a href.html\"=\"\">　</a></td><td class=\"lt\"><a href=\"http://www.amazon.co.jp/exec/obidos/redirect?link_code=ur2&amp;tag=click20thcetu-22&amp;camp=247&amp;creative=1211&amp;path=external-search%3Fsearch-type=ss%26index=blended%26keyword=%25E5%2580%2589%25E6%25A9%258B%2520%25E6%2583%25A3%25E4%25B8%2589\" target=\"_blank\">本を入手</a><img src=\"http://www.assoc-amazon.jp/e/ir?t=click20thcetu-22&amp;l=ur2&amp;o=9\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"border:none !important; margin:0px !important;\"></td><td class=\"lt\"><a href.html\"=\"\">　</a></td></tr></tbody>"
  },
  {
   "type": "raw",
   "tag": "div",
   "attrs": {
    "class": "off"
   },
   "html": "<span class=\"m_r\">エピソード 1</span>調査中。"
  },
  {
   "type": "timeline",
   "rows": [
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　静岡県出身。東大哲学科卒。東京女子師範学校講師、のち教授。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　「幼児の教育」編集主任。「コドモノクニ」編集顧問。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　子どもの「自己活動」「自己発展力」を重視する自然主義的立場をとる。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　「自然物おもちゃ」の活用と「自由遊び」などを強調、幼児教育界に大きな影響を与える。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　戦後、教育刷新委員会委員。日本保育学会を創設、初代会長に就任。"
      }
     ]
    }
   ]
  },
